title: [Warped Wavedancer, Rotted Cabin]
description: Shattered ceiling boards lay scattered across the soggy rug amid tangled kelp, coral colonies, and the bones of long dead aquatic creatures.  Eerie green light filters into the room, its source somewhere beyond the furthest rung of a brass-tacked ladder.  Moldy and mildewed piles of broken furniture are pushed against the slick walls, creating a path that leads to a fissure in the eastern wall.
